        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/f/b77776/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-01-12T22:11:22.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Has anyone seen the below PYCM capsule?</p>\n<p>It\u2019s a darker yellow brown and has the brittleness of Raveneau capsule (unlike the current softer lighter capsules).</p>\n<p>I\u2019ve had the 02 Charmes which has a regular foil capsule similar to the 04s so this raises a red flag.  I wouldn\u2019t expect there to be fakes but I guess you never know.</p>\n<p>Thanks in advance.<br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/8/d/8d38ec7cbb1c91fe6a6676497e9451bbf86056ea.jpeg\" alt=\"C45A3449-828C-4A69-8F7A-22ABF0E6DE63.jpeg\" data-base62-sha1=\"k9jhtSkqoalEFSZo0TDgbrWjgWS\" width=\"1536\" height=\"2048\"></p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 11,
        "updated_at": "2022-06-03T08:31:56.014Z",
        "reply_count": 0,
