        "created_at": "2019-01-12T23:52:29.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I don\u2019t know\u2026and wonder if it\u2019s possible that they decided to do this with a few in France? Maybe some late-release wines? Either way, I think the only way to know is to open one.  If it\u2019s flawed in any way I\u2019d be returning them.</p>",
