        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/jerry_hey/{size}/1033_2.png",
        "created_at": "2019-01-13T02:17:57.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Some of the early PYCM wines (even through 05) had foil capsules, if I remember correctly.  Not sure he started with the wax until a few years after he started his own domaine.</p>",
