        "name": "David Gerstenfeld",
        "username": "David_Gerstenfeld",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/david_gerstenfeld/{size}/1019_2.png",
        "created_at": "2019-01-13T15:34:28.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Fred, I definitely remember drinking some early 2000s PYCM when he was using purchased fruit and they did have those darker wax capsules that were Raveneau like. I have a couple 2005s in my cellar that are foil. I believe he switched to the current wax with his earliest domaine offerings.</p>",
