        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/f/b77776/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-01-13T21:15:51.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Update. This seems to be the real deal.  Excellent wine with some honey richness with a touch of aged notes plus a fine acidic streak.</p>\n<p>Handily outclassed the two Corton Charlies tonight and split with the Roumier for WOTN.<br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/a/4/a4f146eea7145e0da0733b8b883b7a007b79cf88.jpeg\" alt=\"5B8AFCD7-8630-4459-AD49-D4780EB09242.jpeg\" data-base62-sha1=\"nx9eOnhFPdaweteXlf4WNpS1wr6\" width=\"1535\" height=\"2050\"><br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/b/b/bbd87c3c84e5312402699aca30fc2ca078727fa3.jpeg\" alt=\"2F26DFD0-E4BB-4D4A-ADB5-A2FEAD99A2EA.jpeg\" data-base62-sha1=\"qNL6u1XCEXqczprjYGGQEIY6Obx\" width=\"1536\" height=\"2048\"><br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/7/9/793d08a98b2d2775aa96cf957151dfb95c0b8165.jpeg\" alt=\"DE1B7073-5FE6-4A24-B934-B9DFAB978A05.jpeg\" data-base62-sha1=\"hiwxni2gX4xGUIFKBJ61M9WIOVL\" width=\"1536\" height=\"2048\"></p>",
