        "created_at": "2019-01-14T17:23:44.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hey Fred\u2026tell me more about the 04 Roumier CC, as I have a bottle, but have never had one yet.<br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/0/0ff9bfcdb0964982cd3240b6159868fbdf215b1a.gif\" width=\"24\" height=\"18\" alt=\"[cheers.gif]\" title=\"cheers\"></p>",
