        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/f/b77776/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-01-14T17:49:31.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"7\" data-topic=\"148898\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Hey Fred\u2026tell me more about the 04 Roumier CC, as I have a bottle, but have never had one yet.<br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/0/0ff9bfcdb0964982cd3240b6159868fbdf215b1a.gif\" width=\"24\" height=\"18\" alt=\"[cheers.gif]\" title=\"cheers\" class=\"animated\"></p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Open stat. Ours was nice on open but acid fell off quickly at the re-tasting about an hour later. High premox risk.</p>",
