        "created_at": "2019-01-14T17:59:02.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"6\" data-topic=\"148898\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Update. This seems to be the real deal.  Excellent wine with some honey richness with a touch of aged notes plus a fine acidic streak.</p>\n<p>Handily outclassed the two Corton Charlies tonight and split with the Roumier for WOTN.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>That cork makes it look like the wine was poorly stored at some point. Did you notice this?</p>",
