        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/f/b77776/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-01-14T18:07:46.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group quote-modified\" data-post=\"9\" data-topic=\"148898\">\n<blockquote>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"6\" data-topic=\"148898\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Update. This seems to be the real deal.  Excellent wine with some honey richness with a touch of aged notes plus a fine acidic streak.</p>\n<p>Handily outclassed the two Corton Charlies tonight and split with the Roumier for WOTN.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>That cork makes it look like the wine was poorly stored at some point. Did you notice this?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I chose the leaker with lowest fill in case I had to return the rest. The others are in far better condition.</p>",
